# 2. 不思議なサッカーボール

Rin: Wow...! This alley looks totally different from the last one!
Akito: Yeah, you're right. This looks a lot like a street from Argentina.
Len: Huh? What makes you say that?
Akito: I vaguely remember seeing a place like this a few times on TV when I was a kid...
Akito: And... There's another one.
Rin: Oh, yeah!
Len: Another alley, another wall. And it's so big...
Akito: Yeah. It looks just as sturdy as the other ones we saw.
Akito: ...? Something's rolling towards us...
Akito: A soccer ball...?
Akito: What's this doing in SEKAI?
Rin: Len, isn't that the soccer ball Akito gave you that time?
Len: Hmm... No, I don't think so. I didn't bring it with me, and I don't recognize these stains.
Rin: Then... Does that mean someone's feelings also made this?
Akito: This too...? Is there anything our feelings can't make?
Len: Wait, Akito, I bet this was made out of your feelings!
Akito: Huh? Mine?
Len: Yeah! Because you used to play soccer!
Akito: How does that lead to this soccer ball?
Rin: Because... Oh! Because you love playing soccer so much?
Akito: I think you're grasping at straws.
Len: But it probably has to do with you, right? I don't think Kohane and the others used to play soccer.
Akito: Yeah, true...
Akito: Still... What kind of feelings could have made it?
Rin: Oh, I know!
Rin: What if we played soccer together?!
Akito: Huh?
Rin: Playing with it might help shake some things loose in your mind!
Rin: Also, I've been wanting to try playing soccer for a while now! Len always looks like he's having so much fun!
Akito: Wait, that sounds like your actual goal here.
Len: That's just the way Rin is.
Len: But if there is a chance that playing soccer will help you realize something, then it might be worth a try!
Rin: Yay! Take my pass, Akito!
Akito: Got it...! So we're really doing this?
Akito: I still don't think playing soccer here is gonna help. Exploring the other alleys seems like the better option.
Rin: Yeah, I get that! But let's keep playing for a bit!
Len: Akito, pass me the ball! Got it. Now, check out my...tornado shot!
Akito: All you're doing is raising your leg a little higher than normal.
Akito: Whoa, hey! The ball flew way over there!
Len: Oh no! I'm really sorry, Akito! Can you go get it?!
Akito: Alright, fine...
Akito: The flier on that wall over there. Why does it look so familiar...?
Akito: ...!
Akito: Isn't this from...?
